issue.title: oskibot can give you inspirational quotes
issue.body:
For now, oskibot can only give a single default quote. Future iterations will be able to pull a random quote from the quotes.csv in the media folder and give it to the user upon request. 

Committer: Jack Kang <dongwon900@github.com>
